ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of ALEX A. MACBEATH of Murray Harbour, Prince Edward Island, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of History, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Claude Thibault, whose term has expired.
